stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Handshaking: open()
    Idle --> Established: accept_hello() Ok
    Idle --> IdleRejected: accept_hello() Err
    Handshaking --> Established: complete() Ok
    Handshaking --> HandshakingRejected: complete() Err
    Established --> Closed: close()
    Closed --> [*]

    Idle --> WireFault: bus.try_recv() corrupt
    Handshaking --> WireFault: bus.try_recv() corrupt

    state IdleRejected: Result.Err(ProtocolViolation)\nconsumed, no phase advance (ISC-23)
    state HandshakingRejected: Result.Err(ProtocolViolation)\nconsumed, no phase advance (ISC-23)
    state WireFault: Result.Err(MalformedMessage)\ndecode fails before any phase method runs (ISC-24)
